snippet.title: Story Time // Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the Game ► https://store.steampowered.com/app/2002270/Story_Time/

Multiplayer PvP Tactics game. Choose 9 characters. Play with your friends. The player with the most characters wins. Includes local and online multiplayer. Also includes a Story Mode and a Level Editor. Create your own stories. Play them with the world!

Developed by
Plants Can Math LLC​
